dev-1.x.name: drupal/openattribute

security-coverage.message: Dev releases are not covered by Drupal security advisories.

dev-1.x.description: Open attribute is a module designed to allow users to add reuse licenses into their Drupal sites and then provide features so that people using your Drupal site can attribute you. Built to allow users to be as flexible as possible with their licenses, Open Attribute allows you to attribute your entire site / content types with a license and to attribute each node individually if required.

1.1.0.name: drupal/openattribute

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy
